title: Beaver Lodge to host 3D archery Oct. 18
text:
Beaver Lodge to host 3D archery Oct. 18 By Staff | Oct 13, 2015 
Hope â€” Beaver Lodge will host a turkey shoot on its 3D archery range on Sunday, Oct. 18. 
Registration begins at 11 a.m. and awards will be at 4 p.m. Registration is $10 for adults, $5 for youth and younger children can shoot for free on the hillside range. 
For more information, go to the Beaver Lodge website at http://knoxcountybeaverlodge.org/archery.html . Courier Publications' sports staff can be reached by email at sports@villagesoup.com or by phone at 594-4401.
